<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Xu Kai Fan Page</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #1e1e2f, #3a3a6a);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header {
      padding: 40px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .container {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    img {
      width: 250px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .section {
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 10px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 250px;
    }
    footer {
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Xu Kai</h1>
    <p>Chinese Actor & Model</p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="section">
      <img src="xukai.png" alt="Xu Kai">
      <p>
        Xu Kai is a popular Chinese actor and model known for his roles in historical and romantic dramas.
        He gained widespread recognition through hit series and has become a fan favorite for his charm and acting skills.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Popular Dramas</h2>
      <div class="card">Story of Yanxi Palace</div>
      <div class="card">Arsenal Military Academy</div>
      <div class="card">Falling Into Your Smile</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>About Him</h2>
      <p>
        Born on March 5, 1995, Xu Kai started his career as a model before entering the entertainment industry.
        His talent and screen presence quickly made him one of the rising stars in Chinese television.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>Made with ❤️ by Rose</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
